  "title": "Melty Spanish Cheese Jamon Iberico Grill",
  "description": "A savory and romantic Spanish dish featuring Jamon Iberico and melted cheese, perfect for a special occasion. This recipe is onion and garlic free, making it suitable for those with sensitivities.",
