      "name": "Salt",
      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "Black pepper",
      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the raclette grill to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together the white vinegar and olive oil.",
    "Arrange the Jamon Iberico slices on the grill.",
    "Sprinkle the shredded Manchego cheese over the Jamon Iberico.",
    "Add the diced tomatoes and fresh thyme sprig to the grill.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Close the grill and cook for 5 minutes, or until the cheese is melted and bubbly.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Repeat the process for each serving.",
    "Make sure to clean the grill between each use."
